# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Raw lists (may contain PII)
**/lists/raw/
**/lists/cleaned/
**/lists/validated/
**/lists/shipped/

# Reply content (PII)
**/replies/*.md
!**/replies/.gitkeep

# Sync snapshots (large, regenerable)
**/sync/**/*.json
**/sync/**/*.csv

# Performance data (regenerable from tools)
**/performance/results.md
**/performance/health-check-*.md
**/performance/report-*.md
**/performance/debrief-*.md

# Campaign logs (may contain PII)
**/logs/decisions.md
!**/logs/.gitkeep

# Transcripts and meeting notes (confidential)
**/context/meeting-notes/*.md
!**/context/meeting-notes/.gitkeep

# Local Claude Code settings
.claude/settings.local.json

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# Node (if applicable)
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Workspace data (private)
workspaces/

# Planning artifacts
.planning/
